{"tid":266884,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"專家估比特幣今年底前高見4000美元 (06:03)","createTime":"2017-06-01T22:18:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-01T23:17:02.000Z","uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e44f6c9628b92d58c6df62f083615718a6729d51","tid":266884,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T22:18:05.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=Lz%2FlKVMzjY173D09amOymQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=48fddeba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】電子貨幣比特幣(Bitcoin)今年升勢火爆，於上月底一度升至2,791美元歷史新高，其後稍為回落，但最新價格仍處2,370美元的高位，今年以來累計升幅達180%。外媒引述專家分析稱，比特幣今年有望續創新高，年底前或高見4,000美元。<br />\n<br />\n比特幣交易平台XBT Provider主席Daniel Masters估計，今年底比特幣有望升至4,000美元，因為該貨幣正在深入發展至互聯網交易層面，成為程式化的金錢和數碼黃金，其影響愈來愈深遠。<br />\n<br />\n他又指，隨着更多比特幣產品進入市場，相信未來價格波動性將減低，包括比特幣交易所，以及發展有關的沽空市場等。他估計，該貨幣未來交易量將會增加，料可刺激了其價格走高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170602/20170602060328fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170602%2F20170602060328fi.html&d=Lz%2FlKVMzjY173D09amOymQhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=2180911d\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170602/20170602060328fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"080119f6d5d6484d8a195cbc11324773b4bb23b8","tid":266884,"uid":37458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:13:19.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"e6329cc011f9918b8ce5a94eae038672d69b6aa6","tid":266884,"uid":22832,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T23:17:02.000Z","msg":"比特幣專家食屎啦！"}]}